    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/b98e68329fc71cfb61aa49ded42c25df.avif?t=1758626676\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras_big/b98e68329fc71cfb61aa49ded42c25df.avif?t=1758626676 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>托芒的故事：末期</strong> 是一款剧情丰富的RPG游戏。故事设定在一个受东亚启发的幻想世界中。击退恶魔托芒及其爪牙，揭开仇恨循环背后的真相，并终结它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/7789cbb5a296a12e9f85954f48bd86b5.poster.avif?t=1758626676\" width=608 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/7789cbb5a296a12e9f85954f48bd86b5.webm?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/7789cbb5a296a12e9f85954f48bd86b5.mp4?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重温经典的回合制RPG，采用受东亚启发的幻想主题。使用蓄力回合制系统、三角优势机制和列队阵型战斗系统，为战斗增添深度。再加上战争模式的引入，在全军交战中指挥军队展开激战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/0e1f49442aef18e61b78589a42e8f946.avif?t=1758626676\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras_big/0e1f49442aef18e61b78589a42e8f946.avif?t=1758626676 width=800 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/93661f0491e1941130fa6e29551a86f4.poster.avif?t=1758626676\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/93661f0491e1941130fa6e29551a86f4.webm?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/93661f0491e1941130fa6e29551a86f4.mp4?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索地牢的过程中解开谜题，每个角色都带有独特的穿越工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/710be710d02152d2a9c91cfaa15cc1b7.avif?t=1758626676\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras_big/710be710d02152d2a9c91cfaa15cc1b7.avif?t=1758626676 width=800 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/a3a06cd9f37cf0055df8a67702ee68f9.poster.avif?t=1758626676\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/a3a06cd9f37cf0055df8a67702ee68f9.webm?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/a3a06cd9f37cf0055df8a67702ee68f9.mp4?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入战争模式，指挥军队和旅团赢得大型战役的胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/5ea02d26d89d10cf8ff340ba4bc765af.avif?t=1758626676\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras_big/5ea02d26d89d10cf8ff340ba4bc765af.avif?t=1758626676 width=800 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/5071429db159e29cea4c0f9989448ae7.poster.avif?t=1758626676\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/5071429db159e29cea4c0f9989448ae7.webm?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/5071429db159e29cea4c0f9989448ae7.mp4?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放两个或更多角色的组合攻击，扭转战斗的局势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/d94ead3275f642cfdc73a314b6e54fa3.webp?t=1758626676\" width=525 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/fe90cd95a0bf7a25bd3005613b95c3dd.poster.avif?t=1758626676\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/fe90cd95a0bf7a25bd3005613b95c3dd.webm?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/fe90cd95a0bf7a25bd3005613b95c3dd.mp4?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典的像素艺术将陪伴你贯穿整个冒险之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/978db570916e60461013da99067cf849.webp?t=1758626676\" width=525 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/eca2dcf41f8b68fadb2f4298dec15afc.poster.avif?t=1758626676\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/eca2dcf41f8b68fadb2f4298dec15afc.webm?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/eca2dcf41f8b68fadb2f4298dec15afc.mp4?t=1758626676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的游戏决策将影响游戏的结局。谨慎选择，或者探索每个决定和路线，看看通往终点的路上会发现什么！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227810/extras/d44ed7ae51fb19a3d00d9eaef1819aae.avif?t=1758626676\" width=608 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几个世纪以来，一个名为托芒的不死恶魔一直在恐吓联合金龙帝国。由于他的不死之身，每次被击败后，他都会变得更强，从而使人民陷入恐惧与绝望的循环中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，在某一个循环中，当人们正在准备迎战时，托芒却没有出现。认为恶魔已经消失，帝国的人民庆祝了他们的胜利，并重新享受和平的生活。然而，托芒的消失导致了帝国的衰弱。没有了共同的敌人，腐败和内斗在帝国内部肆虐。他们却没有意识到，暗处有一个逐渐崛起的威胁，正准备摧毁帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随一个由各种意想不到的人组成的小队，踏上拯救帝国的旅程，并揭开仇恨循环背后的秘密。他们能成功吗，还是已经为时过晚，无法挽救帝国及其人民？</p>",
